definitions.definition: A person's teens are the period in which they are aged between 13 and 19:
examples: Both my daughters are in their teens.

definitions.definition: the range of temperature between 13° and 19°:
examples: The temperature is expected to be in the teens tomorrow.

definitions.definition: the period of years between 11 and 19 in any century, usually 1911–1919 or 2011–2019:
examples: This type of building was built in the teens and twenties.
